'''Gail Currey''' was the Vice President and General Manager of [[Lucasfilm Animation]] from 2004 until 2008. Previously, she worked for [[Industrial Light & Magic]], where she was credited in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']].

